findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function excludeMultipleAccountsFromFees() uses a loop to exclude multiple accounts from fees and may be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to modify critical settings and parameters, including dividend tracker, Uniswap router address, fees, blacklisted addresses, liquidity, marketing and WBNB reward fees, automatedMarketMakerPairs array, dividends, marketing wallet, gas for processing, and claimWait value.
